    • GameEngine

      public GameEngine​(java.io.InputStream gameFileInput, java.io.InputStream highScoreInput)
      Constructor that try to create game logger every time create a new GameEngine object.

      If fail to create, then catch the exception and give error message or error trace.

      Parameters:
      gameFileInput - The InputStream of the game file to be read.
      highScoreInput - The InputStream of the game high score list file to be read.
